Welcome to the Missing Grade Reporting System

This system is your all-in-one solution for managing grades efficiently and ensuring that no grade goes unnoticed.

How it Works: The system simplifies the process of reporting missing grades and provides a centralized dashboard for tracking your academic performance. Login to access personalized insights and take control of your grades.

Key Features:

  • Dashboard: Gain a comprehensive overview of your academic performance and track missing grades.
  • Grade Reporting: Easily report grades that are not yet recorded in the system.
  • Missing Grades: Keep track of grades that are currently missing from your academic profile.
  • Instructor Contact: Connect with instructors to resolve grade-related queries and concerns.
  • Help and Support: Access resources and get assistance for any issues you encounter.
